&lt;p>We have three living bodies embedded together &lt;br>
But superficially it looks one. &lt;br>
When it comes to nourishing, it is our responsibility to nourish all three. &lt;br>
Consuming food that nourishes the &lt;br>
Only one body and ignoring others is not wise. &lt;br>
